reviews.review_text:
Good solid show Just went through and compared all the sources on 'Other One'.  I think this is the best as of 3/14.  DaWeez and Friend are close seconds.  

Good & spacey out of the drums through Other one.  2nd set song selection is a little lean.  

Still a typically nice and twisted mid 80s excursion.
wowieee I forgot just how intense this Shakedown st was till this morning. Sooo many years later. The ending is rippin feedback vocals echoie vocals fat tempo. dam

Well, Well, Well, You Can Never Tell ... ... what you're going to find in these archives!  My first Dead show! I was a senior in college and remember it well. Thanks for uploading and shaking the old memory cells.
